com.github.errantlinguist.parsers
Class Parser<I,OS,OC>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.errantlinguist.parsers.Parser<I,OS,OC>
Type Parameters:
I - The input object type.
OS - The simple parse output type.
OC - The complex parse output type.
Direct Known Subclasses:
FileParser
public abstract class Parser<I,OS,OC>
extends Object

An abstract class for objects which takes an object as input and outputs another object as a simple parse, and also can create a complex, "complete" parse of multiple such objects. For example, given that a simple parse is a node in a tree, the complex parse is the complete tree structure.

2011-08-06
